title: Jethro Tull - 25th Anniversary Box Set (1993) [4CD] [FLAC]
description:
Release date: 26. April 1993 (UK) and 20. April 1993 (USA) 

DISC 1: 
Various, earlier released albums. 
DISC 2: 
Recorded live in New York City, November 04 - 1970 
DISC 3: 
Tracks 1 and 3 - 5 recorded December 1992 at Ian Anderson&#039;s Home Studio, tracks 2, 6 - 7, 9 and 11 - 14 recorded November 1992 at Beacons Bottom, track 8 recorded December 1992 at Woodworm Studio, track 10 recorded at December 1992 at Presshouse Studio. 
DISC 4: 
Tracks 1 - 2 recorded 19. January 1969 in Stockholm, Sweden, track 4 recorded 05. July 1975 in Paris, France, track 4 recorded February 1977 in London, UK, track 5 recorded April 1982 in Hamburg, Germany, tracks 6 - 7 recorded September 1984 in London, UK, tracks 8 - 9 recorded 10. July 1991 in Leysin, Switzerland, track 10 recorded 20. July 1991 in Tallin, Estonia, track 11 recorded October 1991 in London, UK, track 12 recorded October 1992 in Pullman, Washington, USA, tracks 13 - 14 recorded October 1992 in Chicago, Illinois, USA, track 15 recorded 09. November 1992 in Montreal, Canada. 
Guest musicians: Eddie Jobson (keyboards, electric violin on disc 1, track 15), Maddy Prior (backing vocals on disc 1, track 12).
